<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>מערכת ניהול בית ספר</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
     <style>
        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            direction: rtl;
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            color: #212121;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container-lg {
            max-width: 980px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 16px;
        }

        header {
            padding: 20px 0 16px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }

        .action-card {
            border: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
            padding: 24px 22px;
            min-height: 240px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .action-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .action-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #34495e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .action-card p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #5d6d7e;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #3498db;
            border-color: #3498db;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
            border-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1> מערכת ניהול בית ספר</h1>
        <p>ניהול תלמידות ומורות בקלות ובדיוק</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container-lg">
        <!-- Registration Section -->
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card registration-card bg-light">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="display-1"></div>
                        <h3 class="card-title mb-3">הרשמת תלמידה</h3>
                        <p class="card-text mb-4 text-muted">הוסף תלמידה חדשה למערכת</p>
                        <a href="/register-student" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">להרשמה</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card registration-card bg-light">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="display-1"></div>
                        <h3 class="card-title mb-3">כניסת מורה</h3>
                        <p class="card-text mb-4 text-muted">כניסה למערכת המורה</p>
                        <a href="/login-teacher" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">כניסה</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>